      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Histone Modification: The Epigenetic Code Histone Modification: Unveiling the Complexities of Chromatin Regulation In the realm of molecular biology, histone modification plays a pivotal role in shaping the epigenetic landscape of chromatin.",
