      "factId": "hz.web.b453910f7c183c79.fact.2",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "This intricate process involves the covalent alteration of histone proteins, which DNA wraps around to form chromatin, thereby influencing gene expression without altering the underlying DNA sequence.",
